{
  "stem": "7093.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I was nearly lynched.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I absolutely adamantly said, and it always came true.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And-- and it was just something that happened to me during the war, some-- some extrasensory perception.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I have no idea what it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I still can't explain it, but it was something which-- which happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "As I say then, we were together with my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And my father held my hand for the next five days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "That's to say, seven days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Because two days-- I think we were two days in Sarvar.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "I believe so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I don't know exactly, two days, three days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I don't know exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And then and-- my mother somehow couldn't take it quite in anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And then on the 2nd of July-- I mean, all this happened at the end of June and beginning of July.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And on the 2nd of July, they told us that they are taking us somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And they put us into cattle trucks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Now, the normal load of cattle trucks was 70 to 90.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "They told us that we are going to be special.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And only doctors, solicitors, barristers, architects, and their families will be in that one cattle truck.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And we were 120 in that cattle truck with a bucket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And in the cattle truck, of course, had, like the usual cattle trucks, tiny little-- two tiny little openings.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "We wanted to do it in a civilized way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And so we put our luggage-- we made up rows of our luggage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And we sat down back-to-back, knee-to-knee, pulled-up knees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And that's how we tried to organize ourselves in a civilized way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And that's how we travelled the next five days and five nights.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "The-- obviously, it took some time to accept it that we use a bucket.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
